Class PageAttributes.MediaType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.awt.AttributeValue
      • java.awt.PageAttributes.MediaType
  • Enclosing class:
    PageAttributes

    public static final class PageAttributes.MediaType
extends AttributeValue
    A type-safe enumeration of possible paper sizes. These sizes are in compliance with IPP 1.1.
    Since:
    1.3
